title: july 29: a new dwarf planet
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the discovery of a dwarf planet, Eris. After, she recalls the debut single from Philadelphia native, Pink Sweat$. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
